{"tid":1337190,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察 知法犯法 法例禁止警察工會 警察就成立協會","createTime":"2019-07-21T08:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T12:40:18.000Z","uid":998,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e475172a1c059d7a656d78ed38e9e05f8277c14","tid":1337190,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:24:01.000Z","msg":"法例明文禁止，警察組織工會，警察係政府網頁<span style=\"color: red;\">自己寫到明協會功能等同工會</span>，即係知法犯法，要求有組織罪案調查科調查「香港警務督察協會」是否不合法組織。<br />\n<br />\n//雖然在法例上，警務人員被禁組織「工會」，然而，在功能上，協會和一個「工會」沒有甚麼分別。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/829/chi/n12.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F829%2Fchi%2Fn12.htm&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTecstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=28b2fda9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/829/chi/n12.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCLqmV8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCLqmV8.png&h=a16463e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59a8c15cafc9534cf9d920db31360d33f7af8c59","tid":1337190,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:44:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dab9054b4a9e8a42180087a1c50f0dbf3edadbe5","tid":1337190,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"推到林志偉仆街"},{"pid":"ede6907367625d6605c42a1c7e1ab0cf1870fbf6","tid":1337190,"uid":199532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339d9ddc2134425e412e4964b7178edfda938970","tid":1337190,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:07:56.000Z","msg":"推到警狗回應。<br />\n推到基本法委員會班仆街出來搬龍門"},{"pid":"bd762ccc79e985be26ecd6bcc2e0b5f5a9bf7509","tid":133